blocks.content: Epsilon induction for sets contained in a transitive set. If we are allowed to assume Infinity, then all sets have a transitive closure and this reduces to ~ setind ; however, this version is useful without Infinity. (Contributed by Stefan O'Rear, 28-Oct-2014.)
